import mmcv
from avcv.visualize import *
paths = glob('/data/synthetic/SHARE_SVA_DATASET/val/000/frames/*')
imgs = [mmcv.imread(path, channel_order='rgb') for path in np.random.choice(paths, 10)]
plot_images(imgs)
